{
  "logNo": "224294934011",
  "title": "소상공인의 획기적인 마케팅 방법, 보틀넥, 넥택, 행택을 활용하세요.",
  "addDate": "2026. 5. 27.",
  "categoryNo": "42",
  "url": "https://m.blog.naver.com/cookthedesign/224294934011",
  "content_html": "<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-51a62195-fe82-47f7-85f8-d582c530a982\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-97b991db-bde8-4387-b12b-db116312609d\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-314b6e22-630c-4c68-9dd3-9bf535e7ef35\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>보틀넥 마케팅</b></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-2f593aaf-7933-46d5-bbb0-a4f104fc78e7\" style=\"color:#555555;\">은 음료나 주류 등의 병 목(Neck) 부분에 걸어두는 태그나 사은품을 활용한 오프라인 프로모션 기법입니다. 매장의 수많은 제품 중 고객의 시선을 단번에 사로잡고, 브랜드의 메시지를 직관적으로 전달할 수 있어 최근 외식업계와 주류업계에서 활발하게 사용되고 있습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-0ecb149d-912f-49f7-bbd5-565e629b0770\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-normal\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-justify\" style=\"max-width:595px;\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linkdata='{\"id\" : \"SE-0ecb149d-912f-49f7-bbd5-565e629b0770\", \"src\" : \"https://mblogthumb-phinf.pstatic.net/MjAyNjA1MjRfMTYy/MDAxNzc5NTgzMDcxMTk4.phF1eIplk7axnUye17rUXk2X1XimXB98rslrjURMe3Yg.Fj2RZd9QDebhXvvdYZ5VeSgBZ8dI7ZXzSzAZLQjZny8g.PNG/SE-0ecb149d-912f-49f7-bbd5-565e629b0770.png\", \"originalWidth\" : \"595\", \"originalHeight\" : \"595\", \"linkUse\" : \"false\", \"link\" : \"\", \"fileSize\": \"608891\" }' data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://mblogthumb-phinf.pstatic.net/MjAyNjA1MjRfMTYy/MDAxNzc5NTgzMDcxMTk4.phF1eIplk7axnUye17rUXk2X1XimXB98rslrjURMe3Yg.Fj2RZd9QDebhXvvdYZ5VeSgBZ8dI7ZXzSzAZLQjZny8g.PNG/SE-0ecb149d-912f-49f7-bbd5-565e629b0770.png?type=w966\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-ba385a4c-7451-457f-9a5d-f0132fa3d1e6\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-68138235-8180-4f14-9e0c-502345609afa\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-0810fc65-5d7e-49ad-a1d8-70bfe6ff94d5\" style=\"color:#0078cb;\">■ 이미지 속 사례가 완벽한 이유</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-e5676979-fb8e-4432-9e86-e5c6785aae90\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-1427f0fd-025e-4d30-875f-3c342ce99904\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>· 완벽한 타겟팅과 TPO</b></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-61dad6d4-465f-4e2f-86b0-8c5ab9a7ac82\" style=\"color:#555555;\"> : '돼지 숯불구이 전문점'에서 술을 마시는 고객에게 술을 깨거나 간을 보호할 수 있는 '밀크씨슬'을 제공함으로써, 고객이 가장 필요로 하는 순간(TPO)을 정확히 공략했습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-20dba2bd-1061-408a-b0bb-d8e611ee04e9\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-d70c6604-4879-4829-ac8c-3a889b8c0f98\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-7fbee93b-96e4-4cdb-89ae-a6b28ce67e66\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-bee3bc35-c2ba-4a8a-937e-0ed44f1679fc\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>· 강력한 시각적 효과</b></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-63509513-99ac-4dbf-a0dd-6d01350f6c6c\" style=\"color:#555555;\"> : 단순히 병만 서 있는 것보다, 눈에 띄는 보틀넥/넥택과 알약이 붙어 있어 주목도가 압도적으로 높습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-a5bfcaf2-1c22-44ae-96db-7278ae29a557\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-e7121cf4-9683-4531-88f2-b5285506dca0\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-f7689bf5-2c24-47dc-8411-e55b37c732b9\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-139f9444-999f-4f87-9d4a-8be6093a90ef\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>· 감동을 주는 고객 경험 </b></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-960c34ae-62dc-470d-97bc-4f5f14186613\" style=\"color:#555555;\">: \"내 건강까지 챙겨주네?\"라는 긍정적인 인상을 심어주어 매장이나 브랜드에 대한 충성도(로열티)를 높입니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-431c1f20-e3f2-4921-adc4-70d0f81bf980\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-normal\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-justify\" style=\"max-width:678px;\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linkdata='{\"id\" : \"SE-431c1f20-e3f2-4921-adc4-70d0f81bf980\", \"src\" : \"https://mblogthumb-phinf.pstatic.net/MjAyNjA1MjRfMjM1/MDAxNzc5NTg1OTIwMTYx.X_lD4vpOJS0Oaw7faVkQTFdt9bdH2qwwcWnNJkWFrN8g.69IBGL3qrLkVn9GKF7YCl45tHa_WCtyv0xMIt5sZn4Eg.PNG/SE-431c1f20-e3f2-4921-adc4-70d0f81bf980.png\", \"originalWidth\" : \"678\", \"originalHeight\" : \"1317\", \"linkUse\" : \"false\", \"link\" : \"\", \"fileSize\": \"1289955\" }' data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://mblogthumb-phinf.pstatic.net/MjAyNjA1MjRfMjM1/MDAxNzc5NTg1OTIwMTYx.X_lD4vpOJS0Oaw7faVkQTFdt9bdH2qwwcWnNJkWFrN8g.69IBGL3qrLkVn9GKF7YCl45tHa_WCtyv0xMIt5sZn4Eg.PNG/SE-431c1f20-e3f2-4921-adc4-70d0f81bf980.png?type=w966\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-3a2cb656-f16b-424b-8ed4-a9459abc4f5d\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-21d097b2-0037-4a16-8517-14f9622a23d0\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-3e559942-d74a-4b75-b5ac-3691f6930b91\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-4b0f3209-88bd-4839-89db-0c79ee79192d\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-c9924640-5340-47b2-ae8e-dadbc39f37db\" style=\"color:#0078cb;\">■ 보틀넥 마케팅 기획 시 '주의해야 할 점'</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-cc0f1ab4-5ae0-44d3-9901-4747dcf65c88\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-58c362d0-ebf0-45f4-b2ea-d28e767351b4\" style=\"color:#555555;\">이처럼 효과가 뛰어난 마케팅이지만, 오프라인 인쇄물과 실물 상품이 결합하는 만큼 기획 단계에서 반드시 체크해야 할 주의점이 있습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-4a41aecd-e0d4-42d9-849f-69ee16083457\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-bb53aa0d-9c32-4211-8468-7d6515baf7a5\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-058188c6-0cc7-43e7-9799-66d6f7a15978\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-ff6e0a37-bfe3-4c32-9bf0-d49f36ba6f7f\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>· 규격과 무게의 정밀한 계산 (낙하 방지)</b></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-4390bdbe-b5cd-4776-8524-4a154c42e110\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>​</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-25ef6d8c-c0fa-4def-96e5-fb13ad9ad923\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-5bb0f664-bfef-4157-93e9-0b253829e306\" style=\"color:#ff0010;\">문제점</span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-eae3277d-b2fc-47bc-97b5-f5994109394a\" style=\"color:#555555;\"> : 병 목의 두께는 브랜드(카스, 테라, 진로 등)마다 미세하게 다릅니다. 또한, 하단에 알약 같은 사은품이 붙으면 무게 중심이 아래로 쏠려 타겟이 쉽게 미끄러지거나 찢어질 수 있습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-9124e6d0-f892-4337-8a39-ddada4739122\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-a9c5ce29-a03a-47f1-acca-7885269fd18a\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-afad89ec-b6ef-4ece-a496-6bad070a0ee2\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-bf2cbfa3-3812-40b2-ae5b-e0fc2adf391c\" style=\"color:#0078cb;\">해결책</span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-4f7c0a5c-a41d-4425-b5b4-f20e6b6133fc\" style=\"color:#555555;\"> : 타게팅 할 병의 목 지름을 정확히 측정하고, 종이의 평량(두께)을 최소 250g~300g 이상의 탄탄한 재질로 선택해야 합니다. 접히는 부분에는 오시(누름선) 가공을 넣어 깔끔하게 안착되도록 해야 합니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-99151d13-195f-4a9a-84be-b7b10016336c\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-74707668-376b-4710-9e27-ebc1c183402a\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-b8dfda58-30a3-4a17-984a-64bae4aaebb6\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-69dac715-e665-49b4-aed0-f4aaffbc1354\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#fff8b2;\">(주)파파스컴퍼니은 사이즈에 맞는 칼선을 보유하고 있습니다. 상담 후 주문해 주시기 바랍니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-7d507d4c-16bb-4d8f-9bdf-d5f48b2bfea0\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-d9636a5f-7ca3-4bb8-b918-1a7b8927bf5d\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-e9400256-145e-4684-a53e-98525ca931b4\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-e719b2c5-7eee-497f-a56b-72b384a17fad\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>· 매장 운영(서빙) 편의성 고려</b></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-0916bbbc-f28c-4ecb-a233-2c507f00ed9e\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>​</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-6ed4d56e-319c-4691-b880-4171c238f61c\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-9b444e0c-3cf8-4c91-9b32-c1eda77897e0\" style=\"color:#ff0010;\">문제점</span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-fc2890ea-c865-4cb4-9543-d8b0e8cf78af\" style=\"color:#555555;\"> : 병을 냉장고에서 꺼내거나 손님상에 서빙할 때 보틀넥/넥택이 너무 덜렁거리거나 쉽게 떨어지면 이모님(직원)들의 피로도가 높아지고 매장이 지저분해질 수 있습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-06161022-fe02-4267-b1a4-f7c6d2484d3f\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-d0158f84-836c-42d0-8b87-e8a4f04afb7e\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-e0469bf0-02a9-4b40-8d22-d393afa478cf\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-2a1a2f76-2707-474d-b8fa-2a7a537a7397\" style=\"color:#0078cb;\">해결책</span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-3dc53894-2ca9-4986-9991-293830cd8f9e\" style=\"color:#555555;\"> : 부착형 사은품의 경우, 양면테이프나 접착제가 병의 표면(결로 현상으로 생긴 물기) 때문에 떨어지지 않도록 강력한 접착 가공을 하거나, 애초에 일체형으로 고정되는 디자인을 채택해야 합니다. 구멍에 맞는 디자인을 잘만 선택하시면 이런 유려는 불식할 수 있습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-c01eb854-5222-45fd-9ebd-1709c6078be6\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-e3aa3bfb-1023-46f5-9e0f-b93b41200efc\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-92307b32-dc3a-4019-af34-e18d634010a9\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-9eee92fe-b6bf-4062-9433-f65130a1f2c9\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>· 메시지의 직관성 (가독성)</b></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-987cf719-5639-4e88-b913-2e9a4432a299\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>​</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-39c2a81c-b74c-4b0e-9ab7-7fb316387732\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-323a349c-f2fa-403a-a87a-43820e2e4290\" style=\"color:#ff0010;\">문제점</span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-542b929b-2e30-4b29-a8df-bb34e8d32a4a\" style=\"color:#555555;\"> : 좁은 넥택 공간에 너무 많은 글씨를 넣으면 소비자는 읽지 않고 버립니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-189d5c08-b588-449a-b14a-8468366e78e3\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-905705d0-b06d-4d51-8dd3-65278547d900\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-88cfe390-722f-46b1-9bbf-0808fb533b94\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-normal\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-justify\" style=\"max-width:450px;\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linkdata='{\"id\" : \"SE-88cfe390-722f-46b1-9bbf-0808fb533b94\", \"src\" : \"https://mblogthumb-phinf.pstatic.net/MjAyNjA1MjRfNCAg/MDAxNzc5NTgzNDI5NzA5.pPDi8AwZDfkJJ4rhBz5RCcGnJHN1s1ztxy7OGDrTEEAg.hD_aEGf0GDNp48mTqsnYIyKfIdcSKvcZEruYdEmj524g.PNG/SE-88cfe390-722f-46b1-9bbf-0808fb533b94.png\", \"originalWidth\" : \"450\", \"originalHeight\" : \"1019\", \"linkUse\" : \"false\", \"link\" : \"\", \"fileSize\": \"63629\" }' data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://mblogthumb-phinf.pstatic.net/MjAyNjA1MjRfNCAg/MDAxNzc5NTgzNDI5NzA5.pPDi8AwZDfkJJ4rhBz5RCcGnJHN1s1ztxy7OGDrTEEAg.hD_aEGf0GDNp48mTqsnYIyKfIdcSKvcZEruYdEmj524g.PNG/SE-88cfe390-722f-46b1-9bbf-0808fb533b94.png?type=w966\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-915ae1a7-d7b5-4f4e-b20e-e5eac18b57f0\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-9c24ed8f-e0ed-42f1-b4a3-88a391f77880\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-e72694ae-6bbf-4f09-83af-3aae75665a6c\" style=\"color:#0078cb;\">해결책</span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-048ac098-1f97-471b-b92c-b55816f3f44f\" style=\"color:#555555;\"> : 이미지의 예시처럼 [브랜드 로고] ➡️ [핵심 문구: 간건강/밀크씨슬] ➡️ [효능] 순으로 컬러 대비(레드 포인트)를 주어 3초 안에 핵심이 인지되도록 디자인해야 합니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-e9935e89-397c-4936-a845-b6de0d0045b3\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-4eb74680-5480-4ec5-9761-9267aed36847\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-ef735de4-a9f0-4e1f-9c2c-9f6cc0ed9031\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-c2f225d6-72fb-49b3-b770-7637b91872f4\" style=\"color:#36851e;\">□ 블로그 마무리 멘트 추천</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-dc91a03b-379b-4757-893d-627442230a9d\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-d6740464-c8b0-4252-a0b9-d9d67bcfa03d\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#ffe3c8;\">\"지나친 음주를 막을 순 없지만, 고객의 다음 날까지 걱정하는 디테일! 이런 작은 보틀넥/넥택 하나가 평범한 고깃집을 '다시 찾고 싶은 인생 맛집'으로 만드는 차별화 포인트가 아닐까요?\"</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-quotation se-l-quotation_underline\" id=\"SE-3465631a-c7bf-4159-9cd3-6a18fadc124f\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-quotation se-l-quotation_underline\">\n<blockquote class=\"se-quotation-container\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text se-quote\"><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-a0798fa1-ea55-4f19-8f61-2a7a2066e0d1\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs- se-ff-\" id=\"SE-a5568b89-cf72-4694-838b-5648f0dd28c2\" style=\"\">작업 진행 스토리</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --></div>\n</blockquote>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-962ba346-a784-4796-950f-47764a10f507\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-926be1e5-8176-4073-9ff2-c84e6d9cdfe6\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-69541560-3083-4302-bfc0-11d777cfab98\" style=\"color:#aa1f91;\"><b>■ 견적 및 문의</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-9522d0cb-05e1-469f-8511-aa2659a5f290\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-fit\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-center\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linkdata='{\"id\" : \"SE-9522d0cb-05e1-469f-8511-aa2659a5f290\", \"src\" : \"https://mblogthumb-phinf.pstatic.net/MjAyNjA1MjRfODAg/MDAxNzc5NTg0OTYxMzIz.235pH4KC56lV3Oh_F6G4kDNilytmPrNgEBXCq0nMtigg.fBII1S5OmvKFUa5oDaDzRFHZWBiu44uzM3tfC0lifukg.PNG/SE-9522d0cb-05e1-469f-8511-aa2659a5f290.png\", \"originalWidth\" : \"1003\", \"originalHeight\" : \"1215\", \"linkUse\" : \"false\", \"link\" : \"\", \"fileSize\": \"227734\" }' data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://mblogthumb-phinf.pstatic.net/MjAyNjA1MjRfODAg/MDAxNzc5NTg0OTYxMzIz.235pH4KC56lV3Oh_F6G4kDNilytmPrNgEBXCq0nMtigg.fBII1S5OmvKFUa5oDaDzRFHZWBiu44uzM3tfC0lifukg.PNG/SE-9522d0cb-05e1-469f-8511-aa2659a5f290.png?type=w966\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-47f4d6c0-e457-4754-82f0-64db9b78aceb\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-19d346f8-54e6-4925-a031-6cff5f861e0c\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-3e2049f0-cff5-44ab-87aa-f2ec1935f663\" style=\"color:#555555;\">견적을 문의하고 정확한 고객님의 상담을 통해 사양을 인지한 후 견적서를 제출하게 됩니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-9e85ce02-7b38-4f9e-8c3f-bc9c4e0d4d19\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-3e449c17-0a1d-46f0-8948-c17f52b0e64d\" style=\"color:#555555;\">견적 문의는 네이버 톡톡, 카카오톡, 사이트 문의, 전화 등 다양합니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-talktalk se-l-default\" id=\"SE-53910440-e932-4d17-80ef-bd87a85f4fb8\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-talktalk se-section-align-center se-l-default\">\n<a class=\"se-module se-module-talktalk\" href=\"https://talk.naver.com/w4tbeb?frm=mblog&amp;ref=https%3A%2F%2Fm.blog.naver.com%2Fcookthedesign%2F224294934011#nafullscreen\" onclick=\"sendClickNlog('pst.talktalk', '');\">\n<span class=\"se-talktalk-banner-text\">\n<span class=\"se-blind\">궁금할 땐 네이버 톡톡하세요!</span>\n</span>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-e9e27f28-1022-4d0b-8bf9-5b405fc5e1e8\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-fit\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-center\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link-use se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linkdata='{\"id\" : \"SE-e9e27f28-1022-4d0b-8bf9-5b405fc5e1e8\", \"src\" : \"https://mblogthumb-phinf.pstatic.net/MjAyNjA1MjRfODgg/MDAxNzc5NTg0NjgzOTg3.1MsxixriEV_MSVd3iOy1xg-bNqFL1iz21LussRv5i2og.mZ-efOCtgL80OOpM7Vqnk4q-TNzxy63IFZZ2F-qJpMgg.PNG/00_%EC%B9%B4%EC%B9%B4%EC%98%A4%ED%86%A1_%EC%97%B0%EA%B2%B0%ED%95%98%EA%B8%B0.png\", \"originalWidth\" : \"1773\", \"originalHeight\" : \"887\", \"linkUse\" : \"true\", \"link\" : \"https://open.kakao.com/o/svCsRkwi\", \"fileSize\": \"123062\" }' data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://mblogthumb-phinf.pstatic.net/MjAyNjA1MjRfODgg/MDAxNzc5NTg0NjgzOTg3.1MsxixriEV